libari - a light fontain library
================================
See http://itk.samfundet.no/dok/ari for more/updated information.


Installation from VCS
---------------------
The following procedure installs the latest version of libari into
/usr/lib/python2.4/site-packages/libari/:

bzr branch http://itk.samfundet.no/bzr/jodal/ari/ ari.my-branch/
cd ari.my-branch/libari/
python setup.py install


API documentation
-----------------
Use Python's built in help() function on the modules for documentation.


Usage example
-------------
Turn all diodes on, then off.

$ python
>>> import libari.wall
>>> import libari.canvas
>>> w = libari.wall.Wall()
>>> c = libari.canvas.Canvas(w)
>>> c.blank(99)
(99, 126)
>>> c.blank(0)
(0, 126)
>>> 
